wolf-shaper (Waveshaper plugin with a spline-based graph editor)

Wolf Shaper is a free and open source distortion/waveshaper plugin.
Rather than tweaking abstract knobs, you draw the shaping curve
directly on an interactive spline-based graph, giving instant
visual feedback on how the waveform will be transformed.

Built with the DISTRHO Plugin Framework (DPF), this package
provides CLAP, DSSI, LV2, VST2 and VST3 plugin formats plus a
standalone JACK application.
